obama-in-talks-with-biden-team-on-endorsement-campaign-involvement-report"><img src="https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2020/04/348/196/AP20103733144105.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" alt="Michelle Obama in talks with Biden team on endorsement, campaign involvement: report"></a><div><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div class="info"><header class="info-header"><div class="meta"><!----><div><!----><!----></div></div><h4 class="title"><a href="/politics/michelle-obama-in-talks-with-biden-team-on-endorsement-campaign-involvement-report">Michelle Obama in talks with Biden team on endorsement, campaign involvement: report</a></h4></header><div class="content"><!----></div><!----></div></article><article class="article"><div class="m"><a href="/politics/biden-trump-spar-tougher-on-china-coronavirus"><img src="https://a57.foxnews.com/static.foxnews.com/foxnews.com/content/uploads/2020/04/348/196/Biden-Trump-Split-thumb.jpg?ve=1&amp;tl=1" alt="Biden, Trump spar over who is tougher on China as anger rises over coronavirus pandemic"></a><div><!----><!----><!----></div></div><div class="info"><header class="info-header"><div class="meta"><!----><div><!----><!----></div></div><h4 class="title"><a href="/politics/biden-trump-spar-tougher-on-china-coronavirus">Biden, Trump spar over who is tougher on China as anger rises over coronavirus pandemic</a></h4></header><div class="content"><!----></div><!----></div></article></div><!----></section><div class="ad-container desktop"><div data-ad-pos="desktop" data-ad-size="300x251" data-ad-lz="" class="ad gpt "></div><span class="advert-txt">ADVERTISEMENT</span></div><div data-uid="ar-11" class="vendor-unit"></div></div></div></aside></div></article></main></div><div class="post-content"></div></div><footer class="site-footer"><div class="footer-upper"><div class="section-nav"><div class="inner"><nav aria-label="Coronavirus" class="mobile"><h6 class="nav-title"><a aria-label="Coronavirus" href="/category/health/infectious-disease/coronavirus">Coronavirus</a></h6><ul></ul></nav><nav aria-label="U.S."><h6 class="nav-title"><a aria-label="U.S." href="/us">U.S.</a></h6><ul><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="U.S. - Crime" href="/category/us/crime">Crime</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="U.S. - Military" href="/category/us/military">Military</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="U.S. - Education" href="/category/us/education">Education</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="U.S. - Terror" href="/category/us/terror">Terror</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="U.S. - Immigration" href="/category/us/immigration">Immigration</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="U.S. - Economy" href="/category/us/economy">Economy</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="U.S. - Personal Freedoms" href="/category/us/personal-freedoms">Personal Freedoms</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="U.S. - Fox News Investigates" href="/category/news-events/fox-news-investigates">Fox News Investigates</a></li></ul></nav><nav aria-label="World"><h6 class="nav-title"><a aria-label="World" href="/world">World</a></h6><ul><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="World - U.N." href="/category/world/united-nations">U.N.</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="World - Conflicts" href="/category/world/conflicts">Conflicts</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="World - Terrorism" href="/category/world/terrorism">Terrorism</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="World - Disasters" href="/category/world/disasters">Disasters</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="World - Global Economy" href="/category/world/global-economy">Global Economy</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="World - Environment" href="/category/world/environment">Environment</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="World - Religion" href="/category/world/world-religion">Religion</a></li><li class="nav-item"><a aria-label="World - Scandals" href="/category/world/scandals">Scandals</a></li></ul>